            },
            "effect": "The Looksee Man Strides. He has a +10-foot status bonus to his Speed during this Stride. The DC from shadow blending increases to 11 during this Stride, and the Looksee Man remains concealed by dim light until the end of the movement, even if he leaves dim light during the Stride.",
